# PETN 16240 NVE throughput
units real
atom_style charge
read_data data.reax
replicate 7 8 5
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
pair_style reaxff NULL
pair_coeff * * ffield.reax C H O N
fix qeq all qeq/reaxff 1 0.0 10.0 1.0e-6 reaxff maxiter 1000
fix nve all nve
thermo 100
thermo_style custom step temp pe etotal press
timestep 0.1
run 100
